      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 201,
      "message": "void x(Map <String,Collection<DmiCmSubscriptionKey>> lastSubscriberPerDmi,\n       Map <String,Collection<DmiCmSubscriptionKey>> otherSubscribersPerDmi)\n\n\nSubscriber X \n\nCreate Predicate:\n[ch-1, ch-2]\n[\\a\\b, \\c\\d]\n\n\nNew Class: DmiCmSubscriptionKey : datastore+cm-handle+xpath \n\n1) Map <DMI, Collection<DmiCmSubscriptionKey>> lastSubscriber\n\n- iterate over each DMI and send delete message\n\n2) Map <DMI, Collection<DmiCmSubscriptionKey>> moreSubscribersInvolved\n \n- populate cache with this info and 'PENDING'\n\n\n1) DMI-A CH-1 | a\\b | [X]        -> Need to Tell DMI\n2) DMI-B CH-2 | a\\b | [X,Y..]    -> Accepted without Check\n\n3) DMI-A CH-1 | c\\d | [X]        -> Need to Tell DMI\n4) DMI-A CH-2 | c\\d | [X,Z..]    -> Accepted without Check\n\n5) DMI-A CH-1 | f\\g | [Y]        -> Not relevant  \n\n(Create) Cache View\nX - \n\nDelete X \n        DMI-A\n        - (Create) DmiPredicate for CH-1\n        - Status\n              Pending\n        DMI-B\n        - (Create) DmiPredicate for CH-1\n        - Status\n              Pending",
      "author": {
